```python
def fetch_chutes_miner_endpoint() -> List[ChuteMinerEndpoint]:
    """
    Fetch all chutes including private ones too.
    This endpoint returns all chutes, including private ones with "public": false
    """
    url = f"https://api.chutes.ai/miner/chutes/"

    collected_data = []  # Store all streamed data
    with requests.get(url, headers=headers, stream=True) as response:
        for line in response.iter_lines():
            if line and line.startswith(b"data:"):
                metric_data = line[5:].decode().strip()  # Remove "data:" prefix
                collected_data.append(metric_data)  # Append to list

    return [json.loads(item) for item in collected_data]
```
